<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 12:12:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>照片中的 2023 年：乌克兰的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/year-end/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/2023-in-photos-living-with-war-in-ukraine/0000018c-3eca-d53d-a7fc-beff8b2c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 11:01:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/year-end/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/2023-in-photos-living-with-war-in-ukraine/0000018c-3eca-d53d-a7fc-beff8b2c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军为加沙巴勒斯坦人绘制的令人困惑且具有讽刺意味的疏散地图</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/the-idfs-confusing-ironic-evacuation-map-for-palestinians-in-gaza/0000018c-3b63-de12-a3af-3bef79640000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，该地图将加沙地带划分为 623 个区域，目前正用于指导加沙南部的巴勒斯坦人如何避开危险地区，是尽量减少平民伤亡的关键工具。虽然它是半个世纪前首次制定的</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 10:47:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/the-idfs-confusing-ironic-evacuation-map-for-palestinians-in-gaza/0000018c-3b63-de12-a3af-3bef79640000</guid></item><item><title>现在鹰嘴豆泥被要求参加以色列-哈马斯战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/now-hummus-is-called-to-battle-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-39a5-d11b-a3bf-ffadaab60000</link><description>一份围绕美国食品行业的请愿书将以色列美食视为冲突的主要原因之一。但烹饪领域的文化挪用从一开始就存在问题</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 10:38:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/now-hummus-is-called-to-battle-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-39a5-d11b-a3bf-ffadaab60000</guid></item><item><title>巨大的弹坑、儿童死亡、房屋倒塌：加沙南部无处可逃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/huge-craters-dead-children-collapsed-homes-in-southern-gaza-theres-nowhere-to-flee/0000018c-3e77-d8ec-a79c-ffff72000000</link><description>轰炸的恢复正在将加沙人进一步向南推向拉法，那里有一百万流离失所者生活在拥挤不堪的环境中。人们为了食物和水的供应不足而互相争斗</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 10:22:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/huge-craters-dead-children-collapsed-homes-in-southern-gaza-theres-nowhere-to-flee/0000018c-3e77-d8ec-a79c-ffff72000000</guid></item><item><title>在针对巴勒斯坦人的暴力事件中，以色列军队考虑关闭定居者“山顶青年”部队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/idf-mulls-shutting-down-settler-activist-unit-amid-violent-incidents-against-palestinians/0000018c-3e73-d68f-a38c-3e73ac810000</link><description>以色列国防军“沙漠边境”部队招募的激进定居者士兵袭击和虐待巴勒斯坦人和左翼活动人士，并进行未经授权的搜查和逮捕</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 10:20:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/idf-mulls-shutting-down-settler-activist-unit-amid-violent-incidents-against-palestinians/0000018c-3e73-d68f-a38c-3e73ac810000</guid></item><item><title>考古学家可能在耶路撒冷安条克失踪的城堡中发现了屋顶瓦片</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-12-06/ty-article-magazine/archaeologists-may-have-found-roof-tiles-from-antiochus-missing-citadel-in-jerusalem/0000018c-3e6a-de12-a3af-3fefc46b0000</link><description>安条克·埃皮法尼斯 (Antiochus Epiphanes) 于公元前二世纪在耶路撒冷建造了一座强大的堡垒，并可能使用“异教”瓷砖技术来进一步惹恼犹太人</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 10:08:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-12-06/ty-article-magazine/archaeologists-may-have-found-roof-tiles-from-antiochus-missing-citadel-in-jerusalem/0000018c-3e6a-de12-a3af-3fefc46b0000</guid></item><item><title>没有设备、人员或电力：加沙地带南部的医院因伤病人数过多而不堪重负</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/hospitals-in-southern-gaza-strip-overwhelmed-by-scale-of-wounded-and-ill/0000018c-3e33-d11b-a3bf-febb23d70000</link><description>汗尤尼斯和拉法医院的医生告诉《国土报》，当地情况不断恶化，床位和物资匮乏，并且有可能爆发疾病，导致死亡人数飙升。如果疏散迫在眉睫，医生会问：“我们要去哪里？”我们可以将病人疏散到哪里？</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 09:31:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/hospitals-in-southern-gaza-strip-overwhelmed-by-scale-of-wounded-and-ill/0000018c-3e33-d11b-a3bf-febb23d70000</guid></item><item><title>向汗尤尼斯挺进，以色列军队遭遇加沙战争迄今为止最激烈的战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/sweeping-south-israeli-army-encounters-most-intensive-fighting-of-gaza-war-so-far/0000018c-3bb1-de12-a3af-3bfd0c1e0000</link><description>在加沙地带战斗了两个月后，以色列国防军在汗尤尼斯问题上面临着更加严峻的战斗 ■ 美国和以色列国防军总参谋部认为内塔尼亚胡的行动是出于政治动机 ■ 国防军成立的九年里做了什么知道哈马斯的地下隧道吗？</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 04:00:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/sweeping-south-israeli-army-encounters-most-intensive-fighting-of-gaza-war-so-far/0000018c-3bb1-de12-a3af-3bfd0c1e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列拦截飞向埃拉特的导弹；以色列国防军空袭黎巴嫩真主党目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article-live/netanyahu-rules-out-intl-force-in-gaza-cnn-u-s-officials-expect-war-to-last-weeks/0000018c-3d30-d11b-a3bf-ffb996270000</link><description>以色列军队称，一枚射向埃拉特的地对地导弹在红海被拦截 ■ 巴勒斯坦人报告称在约旦河西岸与以色列军队的冲突中受伤 ■ 以色列国防军称周二又有两名士兵被杀 ■ 内塔尼亚胡告诉人质家属“不可能”后，他们愤怒不已立即遣返所有俘虏 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵被杀；加沙仍有超过 138 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙至少有 15,899 人死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 03:45:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article-live/netanyahu-rules-out-intl-force-in-gaza-cnn-u-s-officials-expect-war-to-last-weeks/0000018c-3d30-d11b-a3bf-ffb996270000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-3c6d-d11b-a3bf-feedb31b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 00:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-3c6d-d11b-a3bf-feedb31b0000</guid></item><item><title>共和党议员的反犹太主义模因：国会更关注犹太复国主义而不是美国爱国主义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/gop-lawmakers-antisemitic-meme-congress-more-focused-on-zionism-than-american-patriotism/0000018c-3c36-d5f2-a5cc-7e368fc40000</link><description>众议员托马斯·马西是唯一投票反对谴责美国反犹太主义抬头决议的共和党人</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 23:27:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/gop-lawmakers-antisemitic-meme-congress-more-focused-on-zionism-than-american-patriotism/0000018c-3c36-d5f2-a5cc-7e368fc40000</guid></item><item><title>什么时候你才能明白？领导层需要女性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/when-will-you-understand-women-are-needed-in-leadership/0000018c-3ba1-dc03-a9ec-3ffb112f0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 22:27:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/when-will-you-understand-women-are-needed-in-leadership/0000018c-3ba1-dc03-a9ec-3ffb112f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对待以色列妇女就像对待孩子一样</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-treats-israeli-women-like-children/0000018c-3ba0-d11b-a3bf-ffa9ff400000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 22:24:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-treats-israeli-women-like-children/0000018c-3ba0-d11b-a3bf-ffa9ff400000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府甚至在战前就正在破坏经济</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/this-israeli-government-was-damaging-the-economy-even-before-the-war/0000018c-3ba8-d5f2-a5cc-7fbcf2410000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 22:02:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/this-israeli-government-was-damaging-the-economy-even-before-the-war/0000018c-3ba8-d5f2-a5cc-7fbcf2410000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对红十字会的愤怒反映了本尼·甘茨的政治问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israeli-anger-at-the-red-cross-reflects-benny-gantzs-political-problems/0000018c-3ba1-de12-a3af-3bed376c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 21:50:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israeli-anger-at-the-red-cross-reflects-benny-gantzs-political-problems/0000018c-3ba1-de12-a3af-3bed376c0000</guid></item><item><title>自10月7日哈马斯-以色列战争爆发以来，超过100万美国人参加了抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/more-than-1-million-americans-participated-in-protests-since-oct-7/0000018c-3bda-d11b-a3bf-fffbed7b0000</link><description>根据最近的一项研究，大多数声援以色列的集会都集中在 10 月 7 日哈马斯恐怖袭击后的第一周，而声援加沙的行动吸引了更多的人群，并继续在全国范围内蔓延。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 21:44:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/more-than-1-million-americans-participated-in-protests-since-oct-7/0000018c-3bda-d11b-a3bf-fffbed7b0000</guid></item><item><title>对于某些人来说，他还不够犹太人。本周他为以色列而死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/for-some-he-wasnt-jewish-enough-this-week-he-died-for-israel/0000018c-3ba0-d11b-a3bf-ffa9dff00000</link><description>州立宗教学校系统官员对一名来自埃塞俄比亚的六岁移民的犹太身份表示怀疑。十四年后，那个因族裔而被迫等待学校录取的男孩，成为了一名勇敢的战士</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 21:24:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/for-some-he-wasnt-jewish-enough-this-week-he-died-for-israel/0000018c-3ba0-d11b-a3bf-ffa9dff00000</guid></item><item><title>大学校长因哈马斯-以色列战争引发的校园反犹太主义而受到美国立法者的严厉谴责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/college-presidents-excoriated-by-u-s-lawmakers-over-campus-antisemitism/0000018c-3b44-de12-a3af-3bcd7add0000</link><description>所有三所大学校长都坚决谴责反犹太主义，并采取了详细的措施来打击反犹太主义，但立法者利用听证会谴责他们的努力，一名共和党成员质疑大学多元化举措是否与“马克思主义、BLM、Antifa 仇恨团体”挂钩</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 20:31:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/college-presidents-excoriated-by-u-s-lawmakers-over-campus-antisemitism/0000018c-3b44-de12-a3af-3bcd7add0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在加沙地带南部哈马斯枢纽汗尤尼斯市发起地面行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-initiates-ground-operation-in-khan-yunis-hamas-hub-in-southern-gaza-strip/0000018c-3ae3-d11b-a3bf-feeb33320000</link><description>哈马斯高级人物和许多总部都位于汗尤尼斯，据估计，这里也是该组织在加沙地带的部队指挥地。以色列国防军一名高级指挥官表示，过去24小时的战斗是“战争开始以来最激烈的”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 19:53:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-initiates-ground-operation-in-khan-yunis-hamas-hub-in-southern-gaza-strip/0000018c-3ae3-d11b-a3bf-feeb33320000</guid></item><item><title>获释的以色列人质告诉内塔尼亚胡战时内阁，哈马斯扣押的俘虏遭受饥饿和性侵犯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostages-tell-war-cabinet-that-hamas-held-captives-suffered-hunger-sexual-assault/0000018c-3abd-dc03-a9ec-3efff69c0000</link><description>作为以色列与哈马斯协议的一部分而被释放的人质分享了有关其对待俘虏的严厉证词。然而，他们的主要批评是针对政府的：“感觉好像你根本不知道那里发生了什么。”你声称有情报，但事实是我们被轰炸了”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 19:33:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostages-tell-war-cabinet-that-hamas-held-captives-suffered-hunger-sexual-assault/0000018c-3abd-dc03-a9ec-3efff69c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>